title: 5 Bed 3 Bath Home for Rent in Champlin, MN
posting_body: ['12036 Porter Drive, Champlin, MN 55316', 'Your Next Place is excited to partner with the owner of this home located in Champlin, MN.', 'This 5 bedroom 3 bathroom home is located in a quiet and family-friendly neighborhood, roughly 5 minutes from Hwy 169.', 'This home was built in 1990 and features over 2,400 square feet of living space.', 'Inside you’ll find a large open kitchen with a granite center island with hardwood floors in the kitchen/dining room combo.', 'Upstairs features 3 bedrooms on one level including a master bedroom with a private bath.', 'In the lower level enjoy the large family room with a wood burning fireplace, 2 bedrooms and a ¾ bathroom.', 'All in a convenient location, close walk to the river with easy access to parks and bike trails.', 'Take advantage of a spacious 2 car garage and peaceful views of the park from your walkout patio in your backyard.', "This home's location also provides access to several school options for all grade levels along with local amenities including; food, shopping and scenic landscapes.", 'Landlord’s requirements and qualifications:', "Move in requirement of first month's rent and security deposit which is equal to the rent.", 'Verifiable positive and stable employment history.', 'Verifiable minimum net monthly income of $7,200 or guarantee of lease / co-signer may be required.', 'Verifiable positive rental history and references with no unlawful detainers or evictions within the last 10 years.', 'Credit score of 600+ (average of the 3 bureaus) or extra deposit / co-signer may be required.', 'No smoking.', 'No felonies regardless of charge type or misdemeanors related to violent crimes, drug sales or distribution, fraud, damage to property, prostitution, or theft within the last 10 years.', 'Occupancy limit of 4 non-related, 5 related.', 'Home is not currently approved for Section 8 housing voucher.', 'Applicants are responsible for verifying all information and qualifications with the landlord / property management company prior to submitting a paid application or signing a lease to rent.', 'Your Next Place works exclusively with renters as a free service that focuses on helping you find the next place to call home.', 'We do not own or manage any of the properties we work with.', 'In our goal to keep the renting process as low cost to you as possible we have clients fill out a Your Next Place application that we ask landlords to accept in lieu of charging you an application fee.', 'Before we view properties we prefer to set up a meeting to go over our application and go into more detail on how we function.', 'If interested in this property please call or respond to this ad to set up a meeting!', 'Your Next Place LLC', 'Lease Terms', '1 year',
